{
  "texts": [
    "We started with one example (P1) and added one example (P2) at a time with three examples as a maximum (P3).",
    "(See prompts in Supplementary Table 1).",
    "After achieving improved performance, we incorporated a chain-of-thought approach, where the model processes its own output one more time, for P3 (P4).",
    "To obtain reliable estimates, we used bootstrapping, a statistical resampling technique, with 10.000 iterations.",
    "All research procedures were conducted in accordance with the Declaration of Helsinki."
  ]
}